    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEARCH ALL - FOXES</h2> is a game in the genre of &quot;hidden object&quot;, in which you need to find all the foxes on a large location drawn in the style of &quot;doodling&quot;. The location shows a Chinese city. In the foreground of the location there is a hypermarket with parking for cars, a small pond and a shopping area (market), and two helicopters are flying in the sky. In the middle of the location there is a long bridge for a high-speed train. Behind the bridge, there is a megalopolis, that is, high multi-storey buildings. On one of these houses sits a giant ferocious fox. Behind the multi-storey buildings, you can see a building from which harmful smoke rises into the sky.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br>- Animation elements on location;<br>- &quot;Doodling&quot; design style;<br>- 100 foxes to find;<br>- Pleasant soundtrack:<br>- The gameplay can be interrupted at any time, and the game will automatically save the result.",
